{{Quote|What's a spinnerfish?|Lando Calrissian, under the alias of Bescat Offdurmin, to the pilot of ''Spinnerfish'' over Corellia|<ref name="exile">''[[Legacy of the Force: Exile]]''</ref>}}
'''''Spinnerfish''''' was a [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] armed shuttle and part of the [[Second Fleet (Galactic Alliance)|Galactic Alliance Second Fleet]] patrolling the [[Corellian Exclusion Zone]]. Officers from the ''Spinnerfish'' boarded the ''[[Love Commander]]'' in an attempt to search the vessel. [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] in disguise then [[Mind trick/Legends#Force persuasion|tricked]] [[Lieutenant/Legends|lieutenant]] officer to give the [[Galactic Alliance Intelligence Service|Intelligence]] access codes to enter the [[Corellian system/Legends|Corellian system]].

